Starscream

Starscream watched Terrorsaur take off.

"Great! Another of us left! That makes four. Who do we have left? Me, 
you Drillbit, Phobia, Goldeneye, Dollen and a near death KitKat. All 
that remains of Megatron's vicious army. And where is our great 
leader? HE SHOULD BE HERE!! HE'S IN CHARGE!!!!"

Starscream walked off and sat on a rock, obviously upset. He looks up 
at the rest.

"5 of us....not including KitKat. My vote for Phoiba still stands. 
Our great leader flees, our second in command his near death, and her 
replacement doesn't want the job. We have to pick between ourselves. 
First to receive 3 votes wins. No voting for yourself. In the event 
of a tie we all vote again but only for the people who tied. What do 
you say?"
